race.comment: DAINTREE BLINDER (3) is in sizzling form lately, rocketing around this track in 21.62 to score two back then following on with a 21.72 win over 390m at this track. Recorded strong figures recently and rates on top again. TUTA PEBBLES (8) finished fourth last time at this track but could not have been more impressive before that in her scintillating 16.32 win at Q Straight over 300m. Expected to feature on best figures. MORE THAN MONEY (2) comes here off a placing in quick time (21.78) over 390m at this track. In form and must include in calculations. CUBAN RHYTHM (6) missed the placings here most recently but can sneak into the finish with the right run.
